events.description: Event featuring the return of Pink Rathian and Black Diablos, event-exclusive equipment, and quests rewarding lots of Zenny.
Hunt Zinogre through a new means introduced with the coming update.

Qualily has been busy continuing her investigation into the anomalies and she needs your help again! She’s back with more investigation requests for you—10 of them in total. Can she count on you to help slay monsters and investigate gathering points? Rewards this time will include Carpenterbugs, Monster Bone+, and other materials such as Dragonite Ore! Ready your equipment and prepare to investigate!

Increase in Diablos activity in desert habitats with reported sightings of Black Diablos. Exclusive Packs with Special Carving Knives will be available to aid in hunts. Hunters can add a Hunter Medal to their collection by completing weekend-exclusive Event Quests. During the following times Diablos and Black Diablos will appear more frequently in Desert Habitats for all hunters HR11 and above, and monsters in all Habitats will reappear in shorter intervals than usual.

As temperatures drop in swamp habitats, increasing numbers of Legiana coming to prey on Raphinos have been spotted. It looks like we can expect more to come! Veiled in frigid air, this monster is capable of a devastating onslaught of attacks. Fire- and poison-element attacks are its weaknesses, so gather your equipment and get ready to investigate! Legiana will appear more frequently in Swamp Habitats for all hunters HR11 and above. During the event, monsters in all Habitats will reappear in shorter intervals than usual.
